 2023-03722023-04-28JUS
ActFederal Courts Act
SubjectAssociate Judges (Federal Court) Regulations
PrecisASSOCIATE JUDGES (FEDERAL COURT) REGULATIONS in order to (1) establish that nine associate judges may be appointed to the Federal Court; and (2) establish that the workload of a supernumerary associate judge is at least 50% of the workload of a non-supernumerary judge.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2023-0083 Publication Date: 2023-05-10
